{"tid":2507882,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"2020／21學年全港流失至少1.9萬學生，校長料澳紐通關後有另一波移民潮","createTime":"2021-04-28T10:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T10:44:35.000Z","uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d203557ba1bd281bb11be801266b534d58b6fb3","tid":2507882,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/SIUSX3HVAJFGTLGMLPROU2O2CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FSIUSX3HVAJFGTLGMLPROU2O2CU%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0sls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=e3bd3cdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FSIUSX3HVAJFGTLGMLPROU2O2CU%2F&h=894a45df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/SIUSX3HVAJFGTLGMLPROU2O2CU/</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博研究報告指，2021年香港將有約1.31萬至1.63萬個家庭通過BNO途徑移居英國。教育局數據顯示，2020／21學年與上一學年比較，全港已流失至少1.9萬名學生。有校長表示，留意到今年退學人數比以往多，暫時未估計到是否已達高峰，惟澳紐通關後或會有另一波移民潮，而退學潮會影響學校運作，籲當局全面審視學生離開情況，計算資助額時提供彈性。<br />\n<br />\n以傳統名校拔萃女書院為例，上學期至3月底已有29人退學，並已取錄約十多名插班生填補空缺。多間名校早前亦宣佈招收2021／22學年插班生，包括拔萃男書院附屬小學、港大同學會小學、香港培正小學等。<br />\n<br />\n直資學校議會主席陳狄安表示，學界觀察到今年退學人數比以往多，部份學生離港升學，亦有部份原就讀國際學校的學生離港後，空出學位吸納包括直資學校學生在內的本地生。他稱難以估計退學潮是否已達高峰，惟相信部份家庭以BNO移英，或將反映在2021／22學年學生人數上，加上另一移民或升學目的地澳紐仍未通關，通關後會否有另一波移民退學潮仍是未知數。"},{"pid":"2498fd7dfd07e8c68fd0110d0204731cb924474d","tid":2507882,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"法官都開到口斬學生係值得鼓勵，點會唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce952fbf9006ab5a3f0869b00379aef1e4e87a5a","tid":2507882,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}